TextEng: I would like to receive a lesson in rogue skills.
Text: 도적 기술에 대한 수업을 받고 싶어요.

TextEng: Me want learn how be sneaky.
Text: 나 몰래 하는 거 배우고 싶어.

TextEng: I would like to ask you some questions.
Me want ask you questions.
I am ready for your challenges.
Me ready for challenge.
Goodbye.
Could you go over the details of the challenge once more?
Text: 시련에 대한 세부사항을 한 번 더 설명해 주실 수 있어요?

TextEng: Me need you explain again.
What can you tell me about the plague?
Text: 역병에 대해 뭘 알려주실 수 있어요?

TextEng: What do you know about the cure for the plague?
Text: 역병 치료제에 대해 아는 게 뭐예요?

TextEng: What you know 'bout plague?
Me want know 'bout cure for plague.
What can you tell me about Lady Aribeth?
Text: 아리베스 경에 대해 뭘 알려주실 수 있어요?

TextEng: What you know 'bout Lady Aribeth.
Simple.
Sorry, I didn't quite get that. Could you repeat yourself?
Text: 미안해요, 잘 못 알아들었어요. 다시 말씀해 주실 수 있어요?

TextEng: Me not understand. You tell me again, kay?
Text: 나 이해 못 했어. 다시 말해줘?

TextEng: Got it.
Can you repeat that?
Maybe you say that again, 'kay?
Okay. What else?
Would you be able to go over all that again?
Text: 그거 전부 다시 설명해 주실 수 있어요?

TextEng: Me want you say that again, please.
Right.
Could you go over that again?
Text: 그거 다시 설명해 주실 수 있어요?

TextEng: Me need you tell me that again.
Go on.
I didn't understand that last part.
Me no get what you just say.
Text: 나 방금 네가 말한 거 이해 못 했어.

TextEng: I understand.
Me understand.
Could you go over that persuasion bit again, please?
Text: 설득에 대한 부분을 다시 설명해 주실 수 있어요?

TextEng: Me want you tell me 'bout persuade again.
I don't need your tutorial. Let's just jump to the challenges.
Text: 튜토리얼은 필요 없어요. 그냥 시련으로 바로 가죠.

TextEng: Me not need you tutorial. Me just want go right to challenge.
Text: 나 튜토리얼 필요 없어. 나 그냥 시련 바로 가고 싶어.

TextEng: Ready.
